01 May. The unity day of nations!

Kazakhstan is a great country with a rich history. Kazakhstan connects Asia and Europe, Kazakhstan is the heart of Eurasia. 
The Kazakhs are considered to be hospitable people, and therefore Kazakhstan is a multinational country. It is home to the nation such as Russian, Uzbek, Dungan, Kyrgyz, Caucasians, Koreans, Ukrainians, Turks, Uighurs, Tatars, Germans and over a hundred other Nations. 
For many years, all of them live in Kazakhstan in peace and harmony.
